name: Captured Prisoner of The Aquaburn Citadel
description:
IDENTITY UNKNOWN. Retrieved from the Citadel during an assassination attempt on the Senator. Prisoner has been UV blinded and encased in a Confusion Cube Helmet, awaiting reintegration into the holding facility.

The Holder of this narrative art will receive 1000 tickets to this Prisoner’s broadcasted execution to distribute to the public. Created by @alexdelia for Artifact.Quest 2021.
